" On linux

"" Download openCV release

"" Before to build OpenCV
	
	install the following package :
	
	* v4l2ucp
	* libgtk2.0-dev 
	* pkg-config
	* cmake

"" Building opencv
	
	* in epitivo svn create "opencv/release" directories
	* next go in release dir
	* Do the cmake here from OpenCV source :
		cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RELEASE -D CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local -D BUILD_PYTHON_SUPPORT=ON _open_cv_source_path_
	* make && make install
	
"" tool.sh = USELESS IF "make && make install" COMMANDS ARE DONE

	Config you path for opencv DIR
